<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201016/e485aad216db41f9a70b676f58745967.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">（ShowMaker仅用过六把发条）</span></img></p>
